<H3> <TI>   Attorney General's Office Announces New Appointments </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA1001191994 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 
0430 GMT 7 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1001191994 </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City XEW Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "24 Hours" newscast] </F>
  [Text] There have been changes at the Attorney General's 
Office. Gustavo Hirales Moranes is the new director of the 
Illicit Crops Erradication Agency and Carlos Santibanez Ramos is 
director of the Federal Judicial Police's Narcotics Department. 

