<H3> <TI>   Internal Security Budget Allocations for 1994 Disclosed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY1301215694 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS in Spanish 
1946 GMT 13 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY1301215694 </F>
<F P=104>  Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Buenos Aires, 13 Jan (NA) -- Budget allocations for 
internal security this year grew by approximately 169 million 
pesos with respect to the allocations for 1993. The figures are 
included in the budget that Congress approved for 1994. 
  The following is a comparative table of the allocations for 
1993 and 1994: 


----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|                  |1993              |1994              |Difference        | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Internal Security |1,214,990,500     |1,353,106,754     |138,116,254       | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|SIDE [Secretariat |159,922,000       |191,800,000       |31,878,000        | 
|for State Intelli-|                  |                  |                  | 
|gence]            |                  |                  |                  | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


  As for the security forces, the following are the figures 
provided for in the 1994 budget: 


------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Federal Police:                       |560,962,000                           | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Border Police:                        |325,121,000                           | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Prefecture:                           |254,789,000                           | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


  If these figures are added to the Armed Forces allocations, 
the total amount destined to defense and internal security 
amounts to 3,582,091,408 pesos, which is equivalent to 8.96 
percent of the 1994 budget. 

</TEXT>

