Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "NTC News" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Attention: A few minutes ago some U.S. military 
planes overflew Barranquilla several times. The control tower 
at Ernesto Cortizos Airport reported that it did not receive 
notification of the presence of the aircraft, adding that the 
crew did not respond to calls from the control tower asking them 
