<H3> <TI>   Gaviria Meets With Minister </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA1701150194 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network in 
Spanish 1432 GMT 17 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1701150194 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Up-to-the-Minute" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Rudolf Hommes, minister of finance and public 
credit, is now meeting with President Cesar Gaviria to assess 
the attempt against his life -- in which he was not hurt -- and 
his security situation. The Presidential Palace and its 
perimeter are under military control, and special security 
measures are being implemented throughout the city. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

