<F P=106> [Interview with Fabio Villegas, government and interior </F>
minister, by Ana Fernanda Valderrama at Narino Palace in Santa 
Fe de Bogota; from the "National" newscast -- live] 
  [Text] [Valderrama] Here is the first reaction by the 
